---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: FAQ
seo:
  title: Frequently Asked Questions | Vandore Heritage
  description: Answers to common questions about our property representation, relocation, and restoration services.
_enabled_editors:
  - visual
  - data
hero:
  eyebrow: FAQ
  headline: Answers for owners, tenants, and partners
  subheadline: Explore the practicalities of working with Vandore Heritage.
  cta_label: Ask something else
  cta_url: /contact/
faqs:
  - question: How quickly can you prepare a property for market?
    answer: We typically complete positioning, pricing, and creative in 14 days. Accelerated launches are possible with in-house staging assets.
  - question: Do you work with overseas sellers?
    answer: Yes. We provide secure virtual tours, notarised document coordination, and regular reporting to keep overseas owners informed.
  - question: Can you manage relocation housing for entire teams?
    answer: We design packages for teams from ten to one hundred people, including interim housing, long-term lets, and cultural onboarding.
  - question: What happens after a restoration project completes?
    answer: We offer optional guardianship programs covering maintenance oversight, trusted vendor scheduling, and guest preparation.
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.eyebrow">{{ hero.eyebrow }}</p>
    <h1 data-cms-bind="#hero.headline">{{ hero.headline }}</h1>
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.subheadline">{{ hero.subheadline }}</p>
    <a class="cta" href="{{ hero.cta_url }}"><span data-cms-bind="#hero.cta_label">{{ hero.cta_label }}</span></a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    {% for item in faqs %}
    <div class="faq-item" data-cms-collection="faqs" data-cms-item="{{ loop.index0 }}">
      <h2 data-cms-bind="question">{{ item.question }}</h2>
      <p data-cms-bind="answer">{{ item.answer }}</p>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

